Thanks for the tip about the Options and Actions windows.  We really haven't seen much slowdown related to it.  <br>
<br>
On the machines that we've tested in house so far, the new UI actually renders faster than the old one in a lot of circumstances.  (Especially comparing both with the inventory windows open.)<br>
<br>
<br>
BTW - If you want to set your windows to all never fade:<br>
<br>
Options (Alt-O), Display, Set both Fader values to 100%.<br>
<br>
Poof.  No windows ever fade. :)<br>
<br>
Thanks for checking it out.  <br>
